==Ancient Greek==

===Pronunciation===
*διδάσκω / didaskō / did-as'-ko
A prolonged (causative) form of a primary verb δάω daō (to learn); to teach (in the same broad application): 

===Verb===
'''διδάσκω'''

# [[teach]].

